1
00:00:06,633 --> 00:00:08,533
[YUKIO]
WE'RE GOING TO HAVE YOU
SPREAD OUT...

2
00:00:08,566 --> 00:00:11,166
TO FIND AND LIGHT SOME LANTERNS
THAT ARE HIDDEN
SOMEWHERE IN THE FOREST.

3
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:15,500
WHOEVER CAN KEEP THEIR LANTERN
LIT AND RETURN IT TO BASE CAMP
IN THE NEXT THREE DAYS...

4
00:00:15,533 --> 00:00:18,466
WILL BE ELIGIBLE TO GO
ON ACTUAL COMBAT MISSIONS.

5
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:19,666
[ALL GASP]

6
00:00:19,700 --> 00:00:22,800
HOWEVER, THERE ARE ONLY
THREE LANTERNS OUT THERE.

7
00:00:22,833 --> 00:00:26,033
THEREFORE, THERE ARE ONLY THREE
SLOTS OPEN TO GO ON MISSIONS.

8
00:00:26,066 --> 00:00:30,133
YOU'LL BLOW YOUR COVER
IN THAT BIG, DARK FOREST,

9
00:00:30,166 --> 00:00:32,833
SO YOU'D BETTER NOT
BE FLAMING UP OUT THERE, KID.

10
00:00:32,866 --> 00:00:34,233
[GASPS]

11
00:00:34,266 --> 00:00:37,166
I WAS THINKING THIS DRILL
IS ACTUALLY DESIGNED...

12
00:00:37,200 --> 00:00:40,766
TO MAKE US COMPETE,
BUT THEN IF WE START
DOING THAT--

13
00:00:40,800 --> 00:00:42,733
WE ARE GONNA BE
AT EACH OTHER'S THROATS.

14
00:00:42,766 --> 00:00:44,500
READY.

15
00:00:44,533 --> 00:00:46,166
[GUNSHOT]

16
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:52,800
[PANTING]

17
00:00:52,833 --> 00:00:54,033
[FLUTTERING]
HUH?

18
00:00:54,066 --> 00:00:56,400
WHOA! WHERE'D ALL THE MOTHS
COME FROM?

19
00:00:56,433 --> 00:00:58,100
[THINKING]
BLOOD-SUCKING MOTHS.

20
00:00:58,133 --> 00:00:59,933
THEY MUST BE
SOME KIND OF CHUCHI.

21
00:00:59,966 --> 00:01:02,433
I HUMBLY APPEAL TO THEE,
OH, GODDESS INARI.

22
00:01:02,466 --> 00:01:06,233
GRANT MY REQUEST.
LEAVE NOT MY PRAYERS TO THEE
UNFULFILLED.

23
00:01:06,266 --> 00:01:09,666
- [GROWLING]
- HEY, NEE, I NEED
SOME BUG-REPELLENT ROUX.

24
00:01:09,700 --> 00:01:11,666
- NEE!
- [GASPS]

25
00:01:11,700 --> 00:01:15,033
NEE? NEE, NEE, NEE, NEE!

26
00:01:15,066 --> 00:01:16,666
[GASPS]
NEE?

27
00:01:18,433 --> 00:01:22,100
- [GASPS]
- [SHIEMI SCREAMING]

28
00:01:22,133 --> 00:01:24,500
THAT'S SHIEMI.
SHIEMI, WHERE ARE YOU?

29
00:01:24,533 --> 00:01:27,866
SHIEMI! SHIEMI!

30
00:01:27,900 --> 00:01:29,700
[GROANS]

31
00:01:29,733 --> 00:01:31,066
[GASPS]

32
00:01:33,533 --> 00:01:35,166
[RIN]
GET LOST!

33
00:01:42,166 --> 00:01:44,466
[CELL PHONES RINGING]

34
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:45,666
MINE'S RINGING TOO.

35
00:01:45,700 --> 00:01:48,300
HMM.
IT'S KONEKOMARU.

36
00:01:48,333 --> 00:01:51,166
HE SAYS HE FOUND
A LANTERN.
[BOTH GASP]

37
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:55,300
"I CAN'T DO THIS ALONE."
HE'S ASKING FOR HELP.

38
00:01:55,333 --> 00:01:58,066
[SHIMA]
WHOA.
UH, YEAH.

39
00:01:58,100 --> 00:02:00,733
THERE'S NO WAY YOU COULD
LUG THIS BACK ALL BY YOURSELF.

40
00:02:00,766 --> 00:02:05,833
ONCE I SAW IT, I REALIZED
WE MUST HAVE MISUNDERSTOOD
THE REAL PURPOSE OF THIS DRILL.

41
00:02:05,866 --> 00:02:10,200
YEAH. FOR THIS DRILL,
WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO HELP
EACH OTHER AFTER ALL.

42
00:02:10,233 --> 00:02:14,166
[CHANTING]
[GRUNTING]

43
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,233
[SHIEMI]
WOW, RIN, YOU'RE STRONG.

44
00:02:17,266 --> 00:02:20,400
[SHIMA]
OKUMURA, WHAT PLANET
DO YOU COME FROM?

45
00:02:23,066 --> 00:02:25,733
UH, HANG ON,
'CAUSE WE'RE DOING THIS.

46
00:02:25,766 --> 00:02:28,666
UH, OKAY.
[SCREAMS]

47
00:02:28,700 --> 00:02:31,733
[BOTH SHOUTING]
IT'S SO HIGH!

48
00:02:31,766 --> 00:02:33,500
ALL RIGHT, GIDDYAP!

49
00:02:33,533 --> 00:02:35,466
[ROARING]

50
00:02:40,433 --> 00:02:43,400
[GROWLING]

51
00:02:43,433 --> 00:02:45,433
HERE IT COMES!

52
00:02:48,533 --> 00:02:50,166
OVER HERE!

53
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:52,233
YOU DON'T HAVE TO TEASE IT!

54
00:02:54,466 --> 00:02:56,266
[SHOUTING]

55
00:02:58,766 --> 00:03:00,266
[GRUNTS]

56
00:03:02,900 --> 00:03:06,466
KAHN!
[CHANTING]

57
00:03:07,666 --> 00:03:09,166
WE DID IT!
WE DID IT!

58
00:03:09,200 --> 00:03:12,733
WELL, NOW THAT
THAT'S OVER WITH.
[CREAKING]

59
00:03:12,766 --> 00:03:13,666
UH--
OH.

60
00:03:13,700 --> 00:03:16,333
[GROANS]

61
00:03:26,433 --> 00:03:29,466
[SCREAMING]

62
00:03:30,700 --> 00:03:34,033
[SUGURO]
OKUMURA!

63
00:03:34,066 --> 00:03:36,300
[THINKING]
OH, CRAP.
I CAN'T MOVE.

64
00:03:36,333 --> 00:03:39,133
- RIN!
- DON'T WORRY ABOUT ME.

65
00:03:39,166 --> 00:03:41,133
I'LL CATCH UP WITH YOU
AFTER I KICK ITS ASS.

66
00:03:41,166 --> 00:03:42,866
EVERYTHING'S COOL.
JUST GO.

67
00:03:42,900 --> 00:03:45,766
THAT SON OF A--
YOU'RE ALWAYS DOING THAT.

68
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:48,166
[CHUCKLES]
MY BAD.

69
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:51,200
YOU DUMBASS!
I'M GONNA HELP YOU,
LIKE IT OR NOT.

70
00:03:51,233 --> 00:03:52,166
HUH?

71
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:54,066
SHIMA, GIVE ME
YOUR K'RIK.

72
00:03:54,100 --> 00:03:55,933
HERE YOU GO.
JUST BE CAREFUL WITH IT, 'KAY?

73
00:03:55,966 --> 00:03:58,133
EVERYONE ELSE, GET READY TO RUN.

74
00:04:03,033 --> 00:04:05,666
[GROWLS]

75
00:04:05,700 --> 00:04:08,433
NAMAH, SAMANTA, VAJRANAM.

76
00:04:08,466 --> 00:04:09,566
HAM MAM!

77
00:04:10,700 --> 00:04:12,466
[CHITTERING]

78
00:04:12,500 --> 00:04:14,166
[GROANING]

79
00:04:16,400 --> 00:04:17,733
COME, K'RIK!

80
00:04:20,700 --> 00:04:22,033
WHOA, DUDE, AWESOME.

81
00:04:22,066 --> 00:04:24,466
COME ON, HURRY UP.
OKAY.

82
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:26,100
[GRUNTING]

83
00:04:26,133 --> 00:04:28,766
THAT'S ALL I CAN DO,
SO GET MOVING.
HUH?

84
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:32,266
[SUGURO]
RUN!
[ROARING]

85
00:04:32,300 --> 00:04:36,600
[RIN]
WHAT HAPPENED?
I THOUGHT YOU KILLED IT!

86
00:04:56,433 --> 00:04:59,066
♪ [MEN SINGING IN JAPANESE]

87
00:06:11,618 --> 00:06:14,251
[ALL PANTING]

88
00:06:18,245 --> 00:06:20,312
[MIWA]
I THINK IT STOPPED CHASING US.

89
00:06:20,345 --> 00:06:22,378
[PANTING CONTINUES]
[SHIMA]
THANK GOD.

90
00:06:22,412 --> 00:06:26,278
HEY, SUGURO,
THANKS A LOT, MAN.

91
00:06:26,312 --> 00:06:29,212
I WAS JUST PAYING
YOU BACK, IS ALL.
FOR WHAT?

92
00:06:29,245 --> 00:06:32,445
I DID IT BECAUSE YOU SAVED
MY LIFE ONCE BEFORE.

93
00:06:32,478 --> 00:06:36,012
I DID IT 'CAUSE YOU WANT
THE SAME THING I DO--
TO DEFEAT SATAN.

94
00:06:36,045 --> 00:06:39,845
AND BECAUSE YOU HAD THE GUTS
TO ADMIT IT
IN FRONT OF EVERYONE.

95
00:06:39,878 --> 00:06:45,745
YEAH, WELL, A MORON LIKE ME
DOESN'T REALLY THINK TOO HARD
BEFORE SAYING STUFF LIKE THAT.

96
00:06:45,778 --> 00:06:49,278
I DON'T THINK
YOU'RE A MORON.
HUH?

97
00:06:49,312 --> 00:06:55,345
BUT STILL, YOU'RE BEING STUPID
IF YOU THINK YOU CAN TAKE
EVERYTHING ON BY YOURSELF.

98
00:06:55,378 --> 00:06:57,545
YOU'VE GOT FRIENDS.
DON'T FORGET THAT.

99
00:06:59,478 --> 00:07:02,045
[SHIMA] YOU GO, BON.
COULDN'T HAVE SAID IT
BETTER MYSELF.

100
00:07:02,078 --> 00:07:06,112
IF YOU'RE GONNA TAKE SATAN ON,
YOU'RE DEFINITELY GOING
TO NEED SOME HELP.

101
00:07:06,145 --> 00:07:08,512
I'M A WIMP,
BUT I GOT YOUR BACK.

102
00:07:08,545 --> 00:07:13,145
COURSE, IF THERE'S
GONNA BE BUGS INVOLVED,
I WON'T DO YOU MUCH GOOD.

103
00:07:13,178 --> 00:07:16,378
- YOU GUYS ARE--
- RIN, WE'RE HERE FOR YOU.

104
00:07:17,978 --> 00:07:19,878
[SIGHS]
RIGHT.

105
00:07:19,912 --> 00:07:23,412
I HATE TO SAY IT, SHIMA,
BUT THIS TIME
YOU WERE TOTALLY USELESS.

106
00:07:23,445 --> 00:07:25,578
HEY! COME ON,
EASY, BON.

107
00:07:25,612 --> 00:07:27,812
I'M DOING THE BEST I CAN,
CONSIDERING.

108
00:07:27,845 --> 00:07:28,912
[LAUGHING]

109
00:07:31,012 --> 00:07:33,912
[THINKING]
WHAT IF EVERYONE FOUND OUT
I WAS THE SON OF SATAN?

110
00:07:33,945 --> 00:07:35,212
BUGS AREN'T THAT BAD.

111
00:07:35,245 --> 00:07:38,145
WHAT WOULD THEY THINK
OF ME THEN?

112
00:07:38,178 --> 00:07:40,278
WHAT WOULD HAPPEN?

113
00:07:44,045 --> 00:07:45,912
OH, THANK GOD!

114
00:07:45,945 --> 00:07:47,512
WE FINALLY MADE IT BACK ALIVE.

115
00:07:47,545 --> 00:07:50,512
CONGRATS, GUYS.
YOU ALL MADE IT BACK
IN ONE PIECE.

116
00:07:50,545 --> 00:07:54,345
WHAT THE HELL?
HOW'D YOU GUYS FINISH
THE MISSION ON YOUR OWN?

117
00:07:54,378 --> 00:07:56,978
I JUST MADE MY FAMILIARS
DRAG THE LANTERN BACK.

118
00:07:57,012 --> 00:07:58,712
TAKARA GOT HERE FIRST THOUGH.

119
00:07:58,745 --> 00:08:02,678
IT TOOK THEM THIS LONG
WITH ALL THAT HELP?
WOW, WHAT A BUNCH OF LOSERS.

120
00:08:02,712 --> 00:08:04,978
WHAT IS TAKARA ANYWAY?

121
00:08:06,678 --> 00:08:07,878
[GASPS]

122
00:08:07,912 --> 00:08:10,145
WHAT'S WRONG?
OW.

123
00:08:10,178 --> 00:08:12,845
HANG ON. IS THIS IT?
EVERYONE'S BACK?

124
00:08:12,878 --> 00:08:15,245
SO NONE OF YOU GAVE UP?

125
00:08:15,278 --> 00:08:18,945
THEN WHO SET OFF
THAT BOTTLE ROCKET?

126
00:08:18,978 --> 00:08:21,578
OUCH.
SHIEMI?

127
00:08:23,145 --> 00:08:26,678
WHOO-HOO!

128
00:08:32,545 --> 00:08:34,578
IT'S THAT GUY
FROM THE AMUSEMENT PARK.

129
00:08:36,712 --> 00:08:37,878
DON'T JUST STAND THERE.

130
00:08:37,912 --> 00:08:40,578
- SHURA!
- [AMAIMON]
GO GET THEM, BEHEMOTH!

131
00:08:40,612 --> 00:08:43,145
- [ROARS]
- IT TOOK HIM LONG ENOUGH.

132
00:08:43,178 --> 00:08:46,612
- [WHISTLES]
- [GASPS]
A SNAKE!

133
00:08:48,712 --> 00:08:50,478
[SHOUTS]

134
00:08:54,012 --> 00:08:55,478
[ROARING]
[AMAIMON]
YAY!

135
00:08:59,212 --> 00:09:00,912
[MEPHISTO LAUGHING]

136
00:09:03,845 --> 00:09:08,012
I THOUGHT I COULD JUST SIT,
RELAX AND ENJOY THE FUN
WITH A NICE CUP OF TEA.

137
00:09:08,045 --> 00:09:10,412
OH, WELL.
MAYBE NEXT TIME.

138
00:09:10,445 --> 00:09:13,478
SHE'S QUITE FORMIDABLE,
ISN'T SHE?

139
00:09:13,512 --> 00:09:15,778
[GROANS]
I'LL KILL HER.

140
00:09:15,812 --> 00:09:20,978
YOU WON'T.
IF YOU KILL EVEN ONE OF THEM,
I'LL MOST DEFINITELY KILL YOU.

141
00:09:21,012 --> 00:09:22,945
RIGHT. I'M SORRY, BROTHER.

142
00:09:22,978 --> 00:09:24,678
I'LL BE MORE PATIENT.

143
00:09:24,712 --> 00:09:27,412
AN ABSOLUTE BARRIER?

144
00:09:27,445 --> 00:09:30,512
YEP. EVERYTHING INSIDE
THE MAGIC CIRCLE IS SAFE,

145
00:09:30,545 --> 00:09:32,578
AND EVERYTHING OUTSIDE
IS REPELLED.

146
00:09:32,612 --> 00:09:34,778
YOU GUYS SHOULD BE SAFE HERE
FOR A LITTLE WHILE.

147
00:09:34,812 --> 00:09:37,578
THAT'S ALL GREAT,
BUT WHAT'S THE DEAL
WITH THAT GUY?

148
00:09:37,612 --> 00:09:40,012
YEAH, MISS SHURA.
IS HE SUPPOSED TO BE
PART OF OUR TRAINING?

149
00:09:40,045 --> 00:09:43,778
[SHIMA] AND DON'T YOU THINK
HE'S A LITTLE TOO TOUGH
FOR US TO HANDLE?

150
00:09:43,812 --> 00:09:45,245
TRAINING'S OVER FOR TODAY.

151
00:09:45,278 --> 00:09:47,778
WE HAVE TO GET READY
FOR AMAIMON'S NEXT ATTACK.

152
00:09:47,812 --> 00:09:49,445
[ALL]
AMAIMON?

153
00:09:49,478 --> 00:09:52,412
[KAMIKI]
DO YOU MEAN ONE OF
THE EIGHT KINGS? THE BAAL?

154
00:09:52,445 --> 00:09:55,178
THE KING OF EARTH?
THAT AMAIMON?

155
00:09:55,212 --> 00:09:58,078
UH-HUH. AND SINCE HE'S
ONE OF THE BIG GUNS,

156
00:09:58,112 --> 00:10:01,945
YOU EXWIRES DON'T STAND
MUCH OF A CHANCE ON YOUR OWN
AGAINST HIM.

157
00:10:01,978 --> 00:10:04,378
EVERYONE GATHER AROUND.
I'M GONNA GIVE YOU GUYS...

158
00:10:04,412 --> 00:10:07,112
A DOSE OF SOME TRIPLE-C
CONCENTRATED HOLY WATER.

159
00:10:07,145 --> 00:10:08,912
BUT WHY--
[SPLUTTERS]

160
00:10:08,945 --> 00:10:10,112
DOES HE WANNA FIGHT US?

161
00:10:10,145 --> 00:10:12,678
YEAH, THIS HAS GOTTA BE
SOME KIND OF--

162
00:10:12,712 --> 00:10:14,278
KIND OF JOKE.

163
00:10:15,178 --> 00:10:17,178
[GASPS]
WHOOPS.

164
00:10:17,212 --> 00:10:19,345
THAT WAS CLOSE.
IT WOULD'VE GOTTEN UGLY...

165
00:10:19,378 --> 00:10:21,578
IF I ENDED UP
POURING SOME ON YOU.

166
00:10:24,412 --> 00:10:27,945
[SHURA]
IN THE BEGINNING, GOD CREATED
HEAVEN AND THE EARTH.

167
00:10:27,978 --> 00:10:31,745
ALL RIGHT.
YOU GUYS ARE GOOD
UNTIL THE HOLY WATER DRIES.

168
00:10:31,778 --> 00:10:34,512
NO MATTER WHAT HAPPENS,
THE DAMAGE SHOULDN'T BE
TOO BAD.

169
00:10:34,545 --> 00:10:37,545
WHAT ABOUT OKUMURA?
AREN'T YOU GONNA
SPLASH HIM WITH SOME?

170
00:10:37,578 --> 00:10:39,178
YEAH.

171
00:10:39,212 --> 00:10:42,245
HE'S SORT OF ALLERGIC
TO HOLY WATER, SO--

172
00:10:42,278 --> 00:10:46,045
ALLERGIC TO HOLY WATER?
I NEVER HEARD THAT ONE BEFORE.

173
00:10:46,078 --> 00:10:48,178
UH, WAIT.
HAS ANYONE SEEN YUKIO?

174
00:10:48,212 --> 00:10:51,712
HE WAS SORT OF GETTING
IN THE WAY,
SO I SENT HIM OFF SOMEWHERE.

175
00:10:54,951 --> 00:10:56,551
[GRUNTS]

176
00:11:02,296 --> 00:11:03,729
[GASPS]

177
00:11:03,762 --> 00:11:05,362
[GROWLING]

178
00:11:05,396 --> 00:11:07,762
[YUKIO THINKING]
SOMETHING'S WRONG HERE.

179
00:11:07,796 --> 00:11:12,529
THESE CHUCHI WERE RAISED
BY TAMERS, SO WHY ARE
THEY ATTACKING US?

180
00:11:12,562 --> 00:11:14,762
WHAT'S GOING ON?

181
00:11:14,796 --> 00:11:16,396
[LINE RINGING]

182
00:11:18,929 --> 00:11:22,229
WHAT THE HELL?
I CAN'T GET THROUGH TO ANY
OF OUR EMERGENCY CONTACTS.

183
00:11:22,262 --> 00:11:24,662
AND I CAN'T REACH
ANY OF OUR TEACHERS EITHER.

184
00:11:24,696 --> 00:11:28,129
AMAIMON'S SUPPOSED TO BE
A BIG SHOT, SO WHAT'S
HE PICKING ON US FOR?

185
00:11:28,162 --> 00:11:31,162
DUNNO. I'M WONDERING
THE SAME THING.

186
00:11:31,196 --> 00:11:32,862
HEY.
HMM?

187
00:11:32,896 --> 00:11:36,429
I DON'T KNOW THE REASON
WHY HE'S DOING IT, BUT I THINK
I KNOW WHO HE'S AFTER.

188
00:11:36,462 --> 00:11:40,196
- IT'S ME.
- YEAH, THAT'S PRETTY OBVIOUS,
BUT YOU DON'T HAVE TO WORRY.

189
00:11:40,229 --> 00:11:43,596
THE BARRIER'S STRONG ENOUGH,
SO EVEN SOMEONE
LIKE AMAIMON'S...

190
00:11:43,629 --> 00:11:45,729
GONNA HAVE A TOUGH TIME
GETTING THROUGH,

191
00:11:45,762 --> 00:11:48,096
BUT THIS TIME
SOMETHING'S DIFFERENT.

192
00:11:48,129 --> 00:11:50,229
I CAN'T SHAKE THE FEELING
THAT HE'S PLANNING SOMETHING.

193
00:11:50,262 --> 00:11:53,162
ANYWAY, IF HE TRIES
TO COME AFTER YOU AGAIN,

194
00:11:53,196 --> 00:11:56,496
YOU'D BETTER TAKE THE KOMA SWORD
AND GET THE HELL AWAY FROM HERE.

195
00:11:56,529 --> 00:11:58,362
THE KOMA SWORD?

196
00:11:58,396 --> 00:12:01,262
FROM HERE IT DESCENDS,
AND TO HIM IT SHALL RETURN.

197
00:12:05,296 --> 00:12:07,096
GO ON.
TAKE IT.

198
00:12:07,129 --> 00:12:08,629
UH, I--

199
00:12:08,662 --> 00:12:10,796
OH, COME ON.
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

200
00:12:10,829 --> 00:12:13,329
YOU WANTED IT SO BAD.
HERE IT IS.

201
00:12:13,362 --> 00:12:16,862
HOLD ON! YOU SAID
YOU DIDN'T WANT ME USING
MY POWER IN FRONT OF ANYONE.

202
00:12:16,896 --> 00:12:18,629
"DON'T BE FLAMING UP," REMEMBER?

203
00:12:18,662 --> 00:12:22,596
SHUT YOUR TRAP, KID.
YOU SPARKED UP
EVEN AFTER I WARNED YOU.

204
00:12:22,629 --> 00:12:24,496
YOU CAN'T HIDE
ANYTHING FROM ME.

205
00:12:24,529 --> 00:12:26,529
[GROANS]
[LAUGHS]

206
00:12:27,929 --> 00:12:30,529
ANYCRAP, IF YOU'RE GONNA PUT
THE HURT ON SOMEONE,

207
00:12:30,562 --> 00:12:32,929
HOW DO YOU EXPECT TO DO THAT
WITHOUT YOUR FLAMES?

208
00:12:32,962 --> 00:12:36,396
I GUESS I--
AMAIMON'S THE KING
OF EARTH, PAL.

209
00:12:36,429 --> 00:12:38,962
HE AIN'T NO BOTTOM FEEDER.

210
00:12:38,996 --> 00:12:42,196
STOP THINKING ABOUT IT.
TAKE IT.

211
00:12:44,996 --> 00:12:47,329
[SHIMA]
M-MORIYAMA?
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

212
00:12:47,362 --> 00:12:48,296
[BOTH GASP]

213
00:12:48,329 --> 00:12:50,496
NO!
SHIEMI?

214
00:12:55,262 --> 00:12:57,562
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA!
SOMEBODY STOP HER!

215
00:13:00,329 --> 00:13:02,262
[SQUISHING]
[SHURA]
WHAT THE HELL?

216
00:13:02,296 --> 00:13:04,396
THAT'S A PARASITE.

217
00:13:07,796 --> 00:13:09,729
SHIEMI!
WHAT DID YOU DO
TO THAT GIRL?

218
00:13:09,762 --> 00:13:13,796
OH, I JUST HAD A FEMALE CHUCHI
LAY AN EGG INSIDE HER,
THAT'S ALL.

219
00:13:13,829 --> 00:13:16,229
IT TOOK FOREVER AND A HALF
FOR IT TO HATCH,

220
00:13:16,262 --> 00:13:18,896
BUT NOW THAT IT'S NIBBLING
ON HER NERVOUS SYSTEM,

221
00:13:18,929 --> 00:13:21,462
THIS YOUNG LADY WILL DO
WHATEVER I TELL HER TO.

222
00:13:21,496 --> 00:13:24,062
- [GROWLS]
- JUMP!

223
00:13:24,096 --> 00:13:27,262
GET BACK HERE, CONE HEAD!
HEY, YOU IDIOT.
COME BACK HERE!

224
00:13:27,296 --> 00:13:28,729
[ROARING]

225
00:13:28,762 --> 00:13:30,129
[GASPS]

226
00:13:30,162 --> 00:13:32,762
[SNARLING]

227
00:13:32,796 --> 00:13:34,462
[ROARS]

228
00:13:34,496 --> 00:13:35,762
[FOOTSTEPS RUNNING]
NO!

229
00:13:35,796 --> 00:13:37,762
[GROANS]

230
00:13:37,796 --> 00:13:40,196
GO GET HIM.
I'M RIGHT BEHIND YOU.

231
00:13:40,229 --> 00:13:41,229
MM.

232
00:13:41,262 --> 00:13:42,729
OKUMURA!

233
00:13:42,762 --> 00:13:44,696
NOBODY LEAVES
THE MAGIC CIRCLE...

234
00:13:44,729 --> 00:13:46,729
FOR ANY REASON,
YOU GOT THAT?

235
00:13:46,762 --> 00:13:47,996
BUT--

236
00:13:48,029 --> 00:13:50,329
[THINKING]
THAT IDIOT. NOT AGAIN.

237
00:13:50,362 --> 00:13:52,362
COME BACK HERE, DAMN IT!

238
00:13:52,396 --> 00:13:54,829
[GRUNTING]
WHAT DO YOU WANT, YOU BASTARD?

239
00:13:56,796 --> 00:13:58,629
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO
TO SHIEMI?

240
00:13:58,662 --> 00:14:01,562
GOOD QUESTION.
HMM.

241
00:14:01,596 --> 00:14:05,529
I KNOW. I'M GOING TO MAKE
THIS PRETTY YOUNG THING MY WIFE.

242
00:14:05,562 --> 00:14:06,796
HUH?

243
00:14:06,829 --> 00:14:08,696
FROM THIS DAY FORWARD,

244
00:14:08,729 --> 00:14:10,896
WILL YOU BE MINE,
TO HAVE AND TO HOLD?

245
00:14:10,929 --> 00:14:14,662
WILL YOU HONOR ME
AND CHERISH ME
IN SICKNESS AND HEALTH?

246
00:14:14,696 --> 00:14:16,562
TILL DEATH DO US PART
AND STUFF?

247
00:14:16,596 --> 00:14:19,829
AND WILL YOU LOVE ME
FOREVER AND EVER
UNTIL THE DAY YOU DIE?

248
00:14:21,662 --> 00:14:27,062
TO SEAL OUR VOW OF ETERNAL LOVE,
I WILL NOW BITE YOUR LIPS OFF.

249
00:14:27,096 --> 00:14:29,529
[GROWLS]
KNOCK IT OFF!

250
00:14:31,229 --> 00:14:34,162
THAT'S NOT FAIR.
I WAS GONNA SAY THE SAME THING.

251
00:14:35,662 --> 00:14:38,796
- [RIN SHOUTING]
- [ALL GASPING]

252
00:14:38,829 --> 00:14:41,229
CUT THE KID SOME SLACK,
YOU ASSHOLE!

253
00:14:41,262 --> 00:14:42,862
[SHOUTING]

254
00:14:48,929 --> 00:14:50,862
AW, COME ON.
WHY DON'T YOU DRAW
YOUR SWORD?

255
00:14:50,896 --> 00:14:54,429
YOU KNOW, YOU SHOULDN'T
TEASE ME LIKE THIS.

256
00:14:54,462 --> 00:14:57,229
THAT GODDAMN SON OF A--

257
00:14:58,796 --> 00:15:00,296
NO! BON, STOP!

258
00:15:00,329 --> 00:15:03,062
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
YOU'RE NOT SUPPOSED
TO LEAVE THE CIRCLE.

259
00:15:03,096 --> 00:15:07,062
[GRUNTS]
BON, TRY TO CALM DOWN,
OKAY?

260
00:15:07,096 --> 00:15:11,196
[HUFFS]
CALM DOWN, MY ASS.
FEED THAT SHIT TO THE DOGS.

261
00:15:11,229 --> 00:15:14,329
RIGHT NOW I'M SO PISSED OFF
AT THAT PUNK,
I COULD FRIGGIN' EXPLODE.

262
00:15:14,362 --> 00:15:15,996
[BOTH GRUNT]

263
00:15:16,029 --> 00:15:18,496
[GROANS]
THIS CAN'T BE HAPPENING.

264
00:15:18,529 --> 00:15:20,129
[MIWA]
SHIMA, WAIT!

265
00:15:20,162 --> 00:15:22,362
UH--

266
00:15:22,396 --> 00:15:23,462
[GRUNTS]

267
00:15:25,029 --> 00:15:26,862
HUH? ARE YOU KIDDING?

268
00:15:26,896 --> 00:15:30,662
COME BACK!
YOU'RE GOING
TO GET KILLED!

269
00:15:30,696 --> 00:15:32,696
UNBELIEVABLE.

270
00:15:32,729 --> 00:15:35,929
THEY'RE CRAZY.
I'M SO OVER THIS.

271
00:15:48,547 --> 00:15:50,047
HUH?

272
00:15:52,747 --> 00:15:54,580
YOO-HOO!

273
00:15:56,880 --> 00:16:01,080
EXCUSE ME, BUT I THOUGHT
THIS GIRL WAS SUPPOSED
TO BE IMPORTANT TO YOU.

274
00:16:01,114 --> 00:16:04,347
IF SHE IS, WHY AREN'T YOU
GOING FOR THE KILL?

275
00:16:05,747 --> 00:16:08,214
[GROANING]
GO TO HELL.

276
00:16:08,247 --> 00:16:13,580
HMM. OH, WELL.
I SUPPOSE I DON'T HAVE
ANY USE FOR HER NOW.

277
00:16:13,614 --> 00:16:16,780
BUT SINCE SHE'S HERE,
MAYBE I'LL HAVE
ONE OF HER EYEBALLS.

278
00:16:16,814 --> 00:16:20,280
- [GRUNTS]
- A COUSIN OF MINE HAS
A PENCHANT FOR THE OCCULT,

279
00:16:20,314 --> 00:16:22,447
AND I PROMISED TO PICK UP
A FEW FOR HIS COLLECTION.

280
00:16:22,480 --> 00:16:25,580
- I'M GONNA--
- [BOTTLE ROCKET WHISTLES]

281
00:16:25,614 --> 00:16:26,747
[EXPLOSION]
HUH?

282
00:16:30,547 --> 00:16:34,347
YOU FORGOT TO INVITE US
TO THE PARTY,
SO WE'RE CRASHING IT.

283
00:16:34,380 --> 00:16:35,914
NO! GET AWAY!

284
00:16:35,947 --> 00:16:39,080
RUN FOR IT, OKUMURA.
WE'LL KEEP HIM BUSY.

285
00:16:39,114 --> 00:16:42,047
UH, I--
I-I'M JUST HERE
TO SAVE MORIYAMA.

286
00:16:42,080 --> 00:16:43,847
SO-- SO YEAH.

287
00:16:43,880 --> 00:16:46,047
DO WHAT I SAID-- RUN!

288
00:16:46,914 --> 00:16:48,414
[FIZZLING]
[GASPING]

289
00:16:48,447 --> 00:16:50,514
[WHISTLING]

290
00:16:50,547 --> 00:16:52,014
[SCREAMS]
UH-OH.

291
00:16:52,047 --> 00:16:54,547
WHAT THE HELL?
YOU HIT MORIYAMA.

292
00:16:54,580 --> 00:16:55,780
HUH?

293
00:16:58,947 --> 00:17:01,047
[ALL]
UH--

294
00:17:03,214 --> 00:17:05,647
- [GASPS]
- [LAUGHS]

295
00:17:05,680 --> 00:17:07,247
[SNORTS]
BROCCOLI.

296
00:17:07,280 --> 00:17:09,114
[LAUGHING CONTINUES]

297
00:17:15,980 --> 00:17:18,147
[SUGURO]
SHIMA!
[MIWA] SHIMA!

298
00:17:22,380 --> 00:17:24,080
NEKO!

299
00:17:25,514 --> 00:17:26,680
[SCREAMING]

300
00:17:26,714 --> 00:17:28,180
KONEKOMARU--
[GASPS]

301
00:17:28,214 --> 00:17:30,414
[BOTH GROANING]

302
00:17:30,447 --> 00:17:32,147
YOU LAUGHED AT ME,
DIDN'T YOU?

303
00:17:32,180 --> 00:17:36,380
[GROANS]
I DON'T GIVE A DAMN
ABOUT YOU, WEIRDO.

304
00:17:36,414 --> 00:17:39,080
THE GUY I'M SUPER PISSED AT
IS HIM.

305
00:17:39,114 --> 00:17:41,080
YA HEAR THAT, OKUMURA?

306
00:17:42,647 --> 00:17:46,447
YOU ACT LIKE YOU DON'T CARE,
BUT THEN YOU HELP SOMEONE.

307
00:17:46,480 --> 00:17:50,114
I THOUGHT YOU WERE A LOSER,
AND THEN YOU GO KICK
ALL KINDS OF ASS.

308
00:17:50,147 --> 00:17:51,980
WHO THE HELL ARE YOU??

309
00:17:52,014 --> 00:17:54,280
WHY DO YOU GO AROUND
ACTING LIKE A HE--

310
00:17:54,314 --> 00:17:55,114
[GROANS]

311
00:17:55,147 --> 00:17:57,380
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

312
00:17:57,414 --> 00:17:59,614
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE SAYING.

313
00:17:59,647 --> 00:18:02,114
- DON'T IGNORE ME.
- STOP!

314
00:18:10,847 --> 00:18:12,247
[THINKING]
YOU GUYS--

315
00:18:12,280 --> 00:18:14,114
[MIWA]
IF YOU'RE GONNA TAKE SATAN ON,

316
00:18:14,147 --> 00:18:16,047
YOU'RE DEFINITELY
GONNA NEED SOME HELP.

317
00:18:16,080 --> 00:18:18,114
[SHIMA]
I'M A WIMP,
BUT I GOT YOUR BACK.

318
00:18:18,147 --> 00:18:20,614
[SHIEMI]
RIN, WE'RE HERE FOR YOU.

319
00:18:20,647 --> 00:18:23,547
[SUGURO]
YOU'VE GOT FRIENDS.
DON'T FORGET THAT.

320
00:18:25,280 --> 00:18:27,680
[THINKING]
AFTER EVERYTHING
WE'VE BEEN THROUGH,

321
00:18:27,714 --> 00:18:29,747
YOU'VE ALL BEEN SO GOOD TO ME.

322
00:18:29,780 --> 00:18:31,714
[FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING]

323
00:18:31,747 --> 00:18:34,014
RIN! IT'S A TRAP!

324
00:18:34,047 --> 00:18:36,014
DON'T FALL FOR IT.

325
00:18:36,047 --> 00:18:37,614
[PANTING]

326
00:18:37,647 --> 00:18:40,214
YUKIO, I'M SORRY.

327
00:18:40,247 --> 00:18:45,014
I-- I GUESS I JUST DON'T GOT IT
IN ME TO KEEP LYING TO EVERYONE,

328
00:18:45,047 --> 00:18:47,147
SO I DECIDED...

329
00:18:47,180 --> 00:18:50,947
I WANT TO USE MY POWER
TO DO SOMETHING GOOD...

330
00:18:50,980 --> 00:18:52,280
FOR EVERYONE!

331
00:18:57,947 --> 00:18:59,647
[GROANING]

332
00:18:59,680 --> 00:19:03,647
- [GASPS]
- [GRUNTS]

333
00:19:03,680 --> 00:19:06,380
[GROANING]
[LAUGHING]

334
00:19:09,814 --> 00:19:12,247
[PANTING, GASPS]

335
00:19:12,280 --> 00:19:15,680
WELL? YOU WANT ME, HERE I AM!

336
00:19:15,714 --> 00:19:17,580
YAY!

337
00:19:17,614 --> 00:19:18,914
[LAUGHS]

338
00:19:18,947 --> 00:19:20,647
[GRUNTING]

339
00:19:22,947 --> 00:19:24,347
HOLY CRAP.

340
00:19:24,380 --> 00:19:27,947
I-IS OKUMURA...
WHAT I THINK HE IS?

341
00:19:27,980 --> 00:19:30,047
THE SWORD.
HUH?

342
00:19:30,080 --> 00:19:31,414
KURIKARA.

343
00:19:31,447 --> 00:19:33,280
[SHOUTING]

344
00:19:34,814 --> 00:19:37,547
[LAUGHING]
IT'S BEAUTIFUL.

345
00:19:37,580 --> 00:19:39,047
[SHOUTING]

346
00:19:40,047 --> 00:19:41,680
- [RIN SHOUTING]
- [AMAIMON SCREAMING]

347
00:19:41,714 --> 00:19:43,314
BURN IN HELL, BASTARD!

348
00:19:45,014 --> 00:19:47,014
[SHOUTING]

349
00:19:48,147 --> 00:19:51,180
[MEPHISTO LAUGHING]

350
00:19:51,214 --> 00:19:53,614
NOTHING'S MORE VULNERABLE
THAN A DEMON'S TAIL.

351
00:19:53,647 --> 00:19:56,047
A GENTLEMAN KNOWS
HOW TO KEEP IT TUCKED IN TIGHT.

352
00:19:58,047 --> 00:20:01,047
THERE'S SO MUCH
YOU STILL NEED TO LEARN.

353
00:20:01,080 --> 00:20:03,914
STARTING WITH YOUR DESIRES,
MY BOY.

354
00:20:03,947 --> 00:20:05,047
[SHOUTING]

355
00:20:07,414 --> 00:20:08,780
GOT IT.

356
00:20:08,814 --> 00:20:10,914
HEY, IS EVERYONE OKAY?

357
00:20:10,947 --> 00:20:12,547
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN
ALL THIS TIME?

358
00:20:12,580 --> 00:20:15,347
WELL, I WASN'T
FARTING AROUND,
THAT'S FOR SURE.

359
00:20:15,380 --> 00:20:17,080
I WAS FIGHTING
AMAIMON'S PET.

360
00:20:17,114 --> 00:20:20,314
WE GOTTA BAIL NOW.
IT'S NOT SAFE HERE.

361
00:20:20,347 --> 00:20:21,547
[GASPS]

362
00:20:21,580 --> 00:20:23,480
[EXPLOSIONS]

363
00:20:23,514 --> 00:20:26,514
[SHURA, THINKING]
AND YOU WANTED ME
TO BABY-SIT THAT MONSTER.

364
00:20:26,547 --> 00:20:28,380
DAMN YOU, SHIRO.

365
00:20:28,414 --> 00:20:31,780
AT LEAST I'VE GOT SOMETHING
TO LOOK FORWARD TO.

366
00:20:31,814 --> 00:20:33,414
[BOTH GRUNTING]

367
00:20:37,314 --> 00:20:40,280
ON ONE SIDE OF THE PATH
ARE DEMONS, PLEASURE SEEKERS--

368
00:20:40,314 --> 00:20:43,314
INCAPABLE OF ANYTHING
BUT DESTRUCTION.

369
00:20:43,347 --> 00:20:47,180
ON THE OTHER ARE HUMANS,
WHOSE VAGUE MORALITY
MAKES THEM WEAK.

370
00:20:47,214 --> 00:20:52,147
I WONDER...
WHICH PATH WILL YOU CHOOSE?

371
00:20:52,180 --> 00:20:54,047
[BOTH SHOUTING]

372
00:20:55,580 --> 00:20:57,247
[BOTH GRUNT]

373
00:20:58,880 --> 00:21:00,214
[GRUNTING]
[SWORD RINGING]

374
00:21:01,980 --> 00:21:03,480
[GRUNTING]
[SWORD RINGING]

375
00:21:05,280 --> 00:21:07,380
HUH?

376
00:21:07,414 --> 00:21:09,680
IS THAT RIN?

377
00:21:09,714 --> 00:21:11,647
[AMAIMON]
UNBELIEVABLE POWER.

378
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:13,580
JUST LIKE FATHER'S.

379
00:21:13,614 --> 00:21:15,480
[GROWLING]

380
00:21:15,514 --> 00:21:16,947
[GRUNTING]

381
00:21:16,980 --> 00:21:19,414
[RIN SHOUTING]
[CRACKS]

382
00:21:19,447 --> 00:21:21,447
[ROARING]

383
00:21:22,447 --> 00:21:24,280
[SCREAMING]

384
00:21:27,580 --> 00:21:31,614
GOOD SHOW.
I NEVER IMAGINED HE'D OVERWHELM
AMAIMON SO COMPLETELY.

385
00:21:31,647 --> 00:21:33,547
[GASPING]

386
00:21:35,414 --> 00:21:39,580
[MEPHISTO]
YOU'VE FOUGHT ENOUGH FOR TODAY.
TIME FOR A GOOD LONG REST.

387
00:21:39,614 --> 00:21:42,914
EINS, ZWEI, DREI.

388
00:21:42,947 --> 00:21:45,614
KUCHEN KUCKUCKS UHR.

389
00:21:46,847 --> 00:21:49,014
- [CHIMING]
- [CUCKOOING]

390
00:21:50,080 --> 00:21:51,847
HUH?
[CUCKOOS]

391
00:21:51,880 --> 00:21:53,914
[AMAIMON SCREAMING]

392
00:21:53,947 --> 00:21:56,614
[SIGHS]
NOW THEN--

393
00:21:56,647 --> 00:21:59,547
[SHOUTING]

394
00:21:59,580 --> 00:22:01,780
[GASPING]

395
00:22:09,647 --> 00:22:11,214
[GROWLING]

396
00:22:11,247 --> 00:22:13,814
THE LAD'S BEEN CONSUMED
BY HIS FLAMES.

397
00:22:13,847 --> 00:22:15,580
[SNARLING]

398
00:22:18,547 --> 00:22:19,747
MY, MY.

399
00:22:21,914 --> 00:22:24,680
YOU'RE SUCH A HANDFUL,
LITTLE BROTHER.

400
00:22:24,714 --> 00:22:27,080
[SNARLING]

401
00:22:28,047 --> 00:22:30,014
[METAL CRACKS]

402
00:22:40,014 --> 00:22:42,647
♪ [WOMAN SINGING
IN JAPANESE]

403
00:24:02,747 --> 00:24:04,414
[MAN #1]
AH, SO BLUE.

404
00:24:04,447 --> 00:24:07,747
AS BLUE AS IT WAS
THAT NIGHT, NO?

405
00:24:07,780 --> 00:24:11,047
[MAN #2]
IS THIS CREATURE I SEE
BEFORE ME THE SON OF SATAN?

406
00:24:11,080 --> 00:24:12,980
[MEPHISTO]
THAT HE IS, YOUR HONOR.

407
00:24:13,014 --> 00:24:15,380
[MAN #1]
I SHALL EXECUTE
THE SPAWN OF SATAN.

